    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for work or play? This car is a solid choice for anyone seeking a reliable ride with plenty of character. While it shows some visible signs of its journeys and typical wear for its age, it remains a sturdy and functional option that gets the job done. It\u2019s the perfect, budget-friendly companion for your daily needs!",
