    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you won\u2019t find another one like this\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, always kept it garaged, and it's seriously spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
