    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example is mechanically superlative, boasting a documented Besian Systems Double-VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement. The chassis is structurally sound with reinforced subframe mounting points and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and poly-bushes for optimized lateral grip. Power is delivered through a perfectly calibrated variable M differential lock. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the interior remains in showroom state. A definitive driver\u2019s car for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Full service history. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title.",
