    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. This car has been garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, never seeing rain or snow. The exterior paint finish is flawless, treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark, rock chip, or blemish. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. It has been a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment, retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the vehicle is perfect, with every service performed ahead of schedule at the authorized dealership\u2014I have a comprehensive binder containing every service receipt and the original window sticker to prove its pedigree. The tires are fresh, and the wheels have absolutely no curb rash. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the moment it rolled off the assembly line.",
